Frank Hausadowski et al. v. Joseph Grossman et al.Opinion filed February 9, 1899.Sol. Levisohn and J. Kent Green, attorneys for plaintiffs in error.C. A. Williams and C. L. Hahony, attorneys for defendants in error.

Error to the Circuit Court of Cook County.

The only question involved in this case is a question of fact, viz., payment.
